e4b-e094-4b7c-a68f-e0cc6ed15b41" alt="Abstract image with a white triangular shape on a pale green background." class="r-vf62lm" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="fbdd924b-2283-4042-a22b-4730ecd2f281" class="r-16sm09b"><div data-rid="3a329f5f-9a23-46a4-8f6b-b6377abf744b" class="r-1cbak7e"><div data-rid="040a4d3b-8ee2-493a-bb03-5b268106887f" class="r-14xo6oj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Margaret did something she hadn't done in twenty years.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="fc15fa8e-8f9e-4161-b54c-a5557de208f3" class="r-1jy9c55 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>"I walked up our stairs. All 14 of them. Without stopping. Without wheezing. I stood at the top and just... breathed."</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="16b2d720-0f6b-47d8-bfc8-5afdd46fe531" class="r-8ufci4"><picture data-rid="3d214c3d-ea72-4bd6-b721-4baf7fadd359" class="r-15fe3bs"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b3f68bb-2f8c-4a5d-b3f8-a4a86935ce07?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b3f68bb-2f8c-4a5d-b3f8-a4a86935ce07?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b3f68bb-2f8c-4a5d-b3f8-a4a86935ce07?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/2b3f68bb-2f8c-4a5d-b3f8-a4a86935ce07" alt="Green plant with flowers and liquid being dropped into a glass of water." class="r-11rmvp1" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="2fd4fb36-1d7f-4284-bcf9-fce68af10168" class="r-1c3q3ar alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The Science Behind the "Green Tongue Lung Purge"</p></span></div><div data-rid="777cfe68-5631-45db-9b70-3a81b4ce3ae2" class="r-1chgy9l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Research published in peer-reviewed journals shows <strong>mullein leaf extract contains saponins that literally break apart hardened mucus</strong>—like soap cutting through grease.</p><br><p>In a <strong>triple-blind clinical trial with 100 participants:</strong></p></span></div><div data-rid="d48cc705-19da-4664-a2b6-bfd92c08036f" class="r-ixv13v"><div data-rid="ca568145-8674-4214-9953-2bc0d3a8d311" class="r-1jmuhap"><div data-rid="c4655199-d62f-4a2b-88ac-80f9b8b0996b" class="r-kslimr"><div data-rid="e8a87b39-6ae9-4ece-a1df-0b68d2f5146b" class="r-1oolmtd alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>81%</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="6c4fd397-2eff-4234-8174-859c5a79f721" class="r-167d2kv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>reported less frequent coughing†</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="7f6fa276-1d02-4b39-8042-f08b53a98419" class="r-q6s0ud"><div data-rid="b02a5504-5f05-431a-a66e-0ec650243a82" class="r-1uxyjq8"><div data-rid="ea72301d-8a31-4f91-8bed-ab92a56964ff" class="r-vp43kl alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>76%</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="4d1de568-59ca-4921-a089-2307ee156d39" class="r-1w1xk5u alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>experienced easier mucus clearance†</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="c44be2c2-65b3-452e-9cd2-9af8612ee44b" class="r-1tv8gbk"><div data-rid="68d51bb4-2522-447f-a79a-a2d305191243" class="r-gnh276"><div data-rid="b129adf3-684d-480a-93e9-7ab0c216b974" class="r-10g4uvc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>30%</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="2f3ff77e-2e0b-4dca-9dbd-53bfe9b09ce5" class="r-19mbavy alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>reduction in fatigue†</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="50408ba4-71e6-4a7e-82ce-16e9fb411c3e" class="r-t9tnik alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>But here's what shocked researchers:</p><br><p><strong>Unlike medications that temporarily open airways while leaving the gunk inside, this actually helps your body EXPEL what's been stuck for years.</strong></p><br><p>Think of it like this: Your lungs are a dirty sponge. Inhalers squeeze the sponge open. This actually cleans it out.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="46eb769c-4e42-4d92-b126-6706b3b140c2" class="r-ut6rxa"><picture data-rid="625d431d-e326-490a-8686-dc3580b6ac43" class="r-1kyhqst"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/5467295c-f74d-45e0-88e3-6f4b39d447c3?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/5467295c-f74d-45e0-88e3-6f4b39d447c3?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/5467295c-f74d-45e0-88e3-6f4b39d447c3?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/5467295c-f74d-45e0-88e3-6f4b39d447c3" class="r-1t3owec" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="ff932b74-a07d-4afe-b6a7-aba5ae5b5cd8" class="r-geoirj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The Combat Medic Who Watched His Grandmother Fight for Every Breath</p></span></div><div data-rid="6326373c-7873-4135-9934-0ef2a90262f6" class="r-f7pkf0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Dr. Chris Jackson was seven years old when he made a promise.</p><p><br></p><p>"My grandma Shuggie sat at our kitchen table, hunched forward, wheezing so loud you could hear it from the living room," says Dr. Jackson, now a Doctor of Pharmacy and founder of Betterbrand. "She was drowning in her own lungs."</p><p><br></p><p>That image followed him through Iraq as an Army combat medic.</p></span></div><picture data-rid="9a60399f-fc14-411f-a944-cb2e3ba61a1e" class="r-hhaoj"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/646d95f1-aa18-43fb-8a44-50c63bff1925?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/646d95f1-aa18-43fb-8a44-50c63bff1925?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/646d95f1-aa18-43fb-8a44-50c63bff1925?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/646d95f1-aa18-43fb-8a44-50c63bff1925" alt="Man in white coat stands behind product display with plants and &#x27;Better Brand&#x27; sign." class="r-hkv67o" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="89927f60-1c0e-4020-b9ac-817685fad346" class="r-95t7hx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>After his service, Dr. Jackson pursued pharmacy school with one mission: find what actually works.</p><p><br></p><p>"Every medication just manages symptoms. I wanted something that addressed the real problem—the gunk that's literally suffocating people from the inside."</p><p><br></p><p>His discovery? Two ingredients used for 2,000 years that modern medicine ignored:</p></span></div><div data-rid="da3299a4-b8e9-4e56-b7eb-83144f781ce3" class="r-1822pti"><div data-rid="5cf65e9a-1e69-4ff5-8cb0-42530478430a" class="r-16de81x"><picture data-rid="1c9a11f3-e76a-4ba2-b8de-9163abc81e2e" class="r-11i84uz"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/8ed00469-a13a-4a48-9b07-56f186eec558?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/8ed00469-a13a-4a48-9b07-56f186eec558?width=300" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/8ed00469-a13a-4a48-9b07-56f186eec558?width=300" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/8ed00469-a13a-4a48-9b07-56f186eec558" class="r-bj30ld" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="157ea10c-43ca-4d04-acf1-7e82f48fc81a" class="r-1s3vpk7"><div data-rid="ba60d27d-ef95-497e-afa6-630f23e34c0a" class="r-16fl6if alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Mullein Leaf</p></span></div><div data-rid="30317cb5-d2e6-4c63-8a53-62da37021b71" class="r-z6xpxc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Ancient Greeks used it to clear lung congestion. Modern research confirms it breaks down trapped mucus.</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="d7ab415d-248e-435c-84d5-cf2ee4cf0fcf" class="r-eydn1x"><picture data-rid="15dfb6d2-9818-4c19-9281-1ddcaf577475" class="r-1242cud"><source srcSet="https://www.trybetterbrand.com/cdn/shop/files/Melisse_Feuilles_FR_2013b_large.jpg?v=1746025968&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://www.trybetterbrand.com/cdn/shop/files/Melisse_Feuilles_FR_2013b_large.jpg?v=1746025968&amp;width=300" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://www.trybetterbrand.com/cdn/shop/files/Melisse_Feuilles_FR_2013b_large.jpg?v=1746025968&amp;width=300" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://www.trybetterbrand.com/cdn/shop/files/Melisse_Feuilles_FR_2013b_large.jpg?v=1746025968" class="r-eh0nj" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="4a1e640f-ef1e-4cb3-88b4-9750c425c577" class="r-1qkjlha"><div data-rid="44392919-44ae-41eb-b88d-67d21ee6cd7a" class="r-qan95k alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Chlorophyll</p></span></div><div data-rid="2685cd47-ba67-43fc-b787-d6ee3e091536" class="r-1aw1g8f alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Nature's internal deodorizer. Helps neutralize and flush out what mullein loosens.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="531c5370-2f5a-48f3-ba40-ec1089b5ecba" class="r-1im6c8g"><div data-rid="d1f3088e-3e24-471a-bf7d-a7b605269f10" class="r-84fykh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>"My Husband Thought I Was Dying"</p></span></div><div data-rid="c41d78a0-88dd-48a4-b835-8ef9f7d99134" class="r-wht86v alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><em>The first 72 hours can be intense. Here's what actually happens:</em></p><p>"Day two, I coughed up something so dark my husband grabbed his phone to call 911," admits Sandra K., a verified customer. "I told him to wait. Because for the first time in years, I could feel my lungs actually clearing."</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Robert M. was more specific:</strong> "Looked like coffee grounds mixed with rubber cement. Disgusting? Yes. But then I took the deepest breath I'd had in a decade."</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Maria L. kept a journal:</strong> "Day 1: Green tongue, loose chest. Day 2: Coughing up dark brown chunks. Day 3: Walked to mailbox without stopping. Day 7: Breathing started feeling more normal"</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="ba5e5014-739e-4026-92e3-529ad84b3a71" class="r-gmurd9"><div data-rid="c2123750-f187-4394-a15e-78c219c1026e" class="r-ochu0r alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The Truth Nobody Tells You About Breathing Problems</p></span></div><div data-rid="2406a6f7-a831-4bf7-a5f8-8cc3bc57f939" class="r-rfaz6h alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><em>If you're reading this, you already know:</em></p></span></div><picture data-rid="280c93a9-c0d3-4851-8adf-8a7bbc2e21a5" class="r-jjuxld"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/fc41226b-35bc-47c5-9c6a-c4be40701add?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/fc41226b-35bc-47c5-9c6a-c4be40701add?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/fc41226b-35bc-47c5-9c6a-c4be40701add?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/fc41226b-35bc-47c5-9c6a-c4be40701add" alt="Elderly man on bench; elderly man playing catch with child." class="r-1afr8cr" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="12bb7aaf-4ef2-443b-adbe-008ee3a8c3ee" class="r-8fiemq"><div data-rid="348e2da1-3351-4f47-9611-17ab976446aa" class="r-1w0e274"><picture data-rid="9fc70577-0ab7-4f5b-a6c6-f3fa7c9cff12" class="r-1lp4y92"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=50" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=60" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=60" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c" class="r-1khhaa2" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="ec50bf7b-7801-48c9-b7ef-e1ec69a2a296" class="r-evhlk3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong>Morning is hell.</strong> That first cough that turns into five minutes of hacking while your spouse pretends to sleep.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="42589c72-32aa-4357-bdd8-3f9a1b0c98c5" class="r-12ialqf"><picture data-rid="1c0002fc-e907-47b1-8a34-58b0ce1e0619" class="r-15ysar2"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=50" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=60" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=60" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c" class="r-rcokqx" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="2277c748-e9ef-4976-b0c5-572abecee581" class="r-1qopmi7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong>Stairs are the enemy.</strong> You map out routes to avoid them. You've mastered the art of looking busy on your phone while secretly catching your breath.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="39da5a76-af77-4383-9765-ea229bbe32d6" class="r-svmyyj"><picture data-rid="47222d64-2da0-4c0c-8023-fd467133aa61" class="r-19npoji"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=50" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=60" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=60" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c" class="r-1p9s7uf" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="173ee52b-de82-4fa6-964e-ac9a7a798b47" class="r-16y7oaz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong>You've become "that person."</strong> The one who coughs through conversations. Who can't keep up. Who everyone worries about but nobody knows how to help.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="c5321d32-dece-4ab3-948a-c5ad347edbe6" class="r-1q1erb6"><picture data-rid="a33cdfb5-c5ba-4660-89e1-ef68738d8482" class="r-yt3djm"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=50" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=60" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=60" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c" class="r-17gi5ha" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="16b44212-3fbd-4016-aa01-e55a61c82622" class="r-1a2p1el alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong>You've tried everything.</strong> Different inhalers, treatments, exercises. Some help temporarily. Nothing really fixes the underlying problem.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="bc90f417-bec2-40f3-9bed-6311954eaf53" class="r-1267wy1"><picture data-rid="c9fd9867-d62c-4b8f-a909-c93a75f52445" class="r-ajjor3"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=50" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=60" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c?width=60" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/1e5bc658-d2dd-4185-9134-f9e01d19734f/18b50a9c-7840-4408-8434-10d85a5e503c" class="r-6ggko3" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="92216fbe-6e1b-4fb7-824e-dc7a2a99ec97" class="r-xbusnf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong>You measure life differently now.</strong> Not in years but in how many steps before you need to rest. How many words you can say before running out of breath.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="3f7b0449-4e7d-44c5-be43-d88a7b551ef6" class="r-1rxga6h"><div data-rid="82f44cd9-bdae-4816-8eab-a8175e655b61" class="r-1voa3vt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The Viral Videos That Started Everything</p></span></div><div data-rid="768a989c-10c5-4360-a4e2-bc847e7ccd25" class="r-ighhq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>It started with one video. Someone showing their green tongue, then documenting what they coughed up over three days.</p><br><p>Millions of views. Thousands trying it. All showing the same thing:</p></span></div><div data-rid="bc690d1d-7d09-47d3-a6db-0056ad53197e" class="r-1w60k4m"><div data-rid="01951033-5827-4ff8-b4c8-2c55fa437e3c" class="r-1higxem"><div data-rid="9bd6989a-c3e7-43f0-9a55-7918da49e90e" class="r-u3e8gh"><div data-rid="61e83b42-c6cd-4697-aa79-2f0245aecba0" class="r-1bmlhnl alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Day 1</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="a1c54314-cb35-4a41-a287-028bf83f0747" class="r-144ae3e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Green tongue, loosening chest</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="269fa50b-6afa-4126-9400-c358019da9e4" class="r-1vlpqjm"><div data-rid="4261713a-58a9-4a5a-9a21-a9f12543290b" class="r-1pe6nzt"><div data-rid="4a803399-22a3-4efd-af6a-c1a81f9f307f" class="r-g93pcr alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Day 2-3</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="76697812-2dd5-4623-a1e9-1f922ec8cb2b" class="r-g4od6x alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The "purge"—dark mucus, chunks, decades of buildup</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="8392b5a8-cc09-4e4d-8b31-755eb47b33a6" class="r-1q2zcjd"><div data-rid="93434426-04a2-461b-8365-45f789873aa7" class="r-140231n"><div data-rid="301157a9-4ae6-4a1d-8660-b1a50159bac7" class="r-1feio0x alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Week 1</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="477374d9-1cf2-471c-9106-4b1d14e81207" class="r-10yj7gd alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Breathing improving dramatically</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="641def21-b350-45e2-af18-692e91fe85c5" class="r-18e41b9"><div data-rid="c1dc52f9-9383-440c-b759-39458f60a666" class="r-ayoo